	sprite engine.

@{b}   INPUTS@{ub}
       vp - pointer to ViewPort structure that this sprite is
		  relative to,  or 0 if relative only top of View
	oldsprite - pointer the old ExtSprite structure
	newsprite - pointer to the new ExtSprite structure. 

